headline: Watch Live: Donald Trump Holds Save America Rally in Commerce, Georgia
author: Ethan Letkeman
sentences:
Other speakers include:
State Sen. Burt Jones  Lieutenant Governor candidate
Rep. Jody Hice (R-GA)  Secretary of State candidate
Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene (R-GA)
Rep. Andrew Clyde (R-GA)
Vernon Jones  Former state Rep. and current U.S. House candidate
John Gordon  Attorney General candidate
Patrick Witt  Insurance and Safety Fire Commissioner candidate
Tom Homan  Former acting director of Immigration and Customs Enforcement
Todd Starnes  Columnist and radio-host

Multiple Trump-endorsed candidates are scheduled to speak at Saturdays rally, including former football star and current Republican primary Senate candidate Herschel Walker and former Senator and current gubernatorial candidate David Perdue.
Former President Donald Trump will hold a Save America Rally in Commerce, Georgia, on Saturday, March 26.
Trump is scheduled to speak at 7:00 P.M. Eastern.
